{"tid":2044334,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［行動？］依家Twitter 可行嘅一條出路","createTime":"2020-05-31T05:01:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-31T06:04:37.000Z","uid":42108,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1af926ab346d323df6f4d5ee83994f72a6fc0555","tid":2044334,"uid":42108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T05:01:02.000Z","msg":"依家美國各州黑人示威越演越烈<br />\n我見到唔少人都開post話文宣要暫時撤退<br />\n但係見到班五毛係twitter spin緊香港抗爭<br />\n我覺得可以諗下可行嘅辦法黎抵消佢地<br />\n所以我諗左一個方法<br />\n可能大家唔洗係到坐以待斃<br />\n就係<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">放大香港警暴問題</span></span><br />\n我地可以用對比圖形式比較今次<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港黑警</span></span> 同埋<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">美國警察</span></span> <br />\n嘅示威處理手法<br />\n咁樣就可以避免涉及太多政治但係又唔至於會比班五毛spin到話我地係暴徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 諗住討論成效先決定實行"},{"pid":"b3d68e8db5c4a89931c4955839c10b4a08fc1e3c","tid":2044334,"uid":42108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T05:01:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4e630571858c995e2697e2be917160659cc5d42c","tid":2044334,"uid":42108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T05:01:35.000Z","msg":"可以參考下依家美國州份有警察參與示威者遊行"},{"pid":"081ebde963f05631b1863ba7a642965aa0f773bf","tid":2044334,"uid":42108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e630571858c995e2697e2be917160659cc5d42c","tid":2044334,"uid":42108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T05:01:35.000Z","msg":"可以參考下依家美國州份有警察參與示威者遊行"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T05:01:59.000Z","msg":"警察不再止暴制亂，反而參與示威者遊行並支持其訴求<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2044143\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2044143</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4fe20443cbbb9c9434a326e38d01ba5e815d1dd9","tid":2044334,"uid":42108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-3